{"_path":"/tags/textformats/h5","_dir":"textformats","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"H5","description":"H5（HTML5）是HTML的第五个版本，是对HTML标准的更新和扩展。HTML5引入了许多新的特性和功能，使得Web开发变得更加强大和灵活。HTML5是一个强大且灵活的标准，为开发者提供了丰富的功能和工具，使得构建现代化、交互式的Web页面和应用程序变得更加容易和高效","name":"h5","icon":"logos:html-5","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"HTML5是最新的HTML标准，用于构建Web页面和应用程序。以下是HTML5的一些关键特点："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语义化标记"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：HTML5引入了许多新的语义化元素（如"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<header>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<footer>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<nav>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"等），使得页面结构更清晰、易于理解和维护。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多媒体支持"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：HTML5提供了内置的多媒体元素（如"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<audio>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<video>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"），使得在网页中嵌入音频和视频变得更加简单。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Canvas和SVG"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：HTML5引入了"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"<canvas>"}]},{"type":"text","value":"元素和SVG（Scalable Vector Graphics）标准，使得在网页中绘制图形和动画变得更加灵活和强大。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","pro